{"tid":49934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[俠義風骨] 尼日利亞7歲女童發動自殺式炸彈襲擊","createTime":"2016-12-22T05:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T11:28:15.000Z","uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c021c47c33df8332d57379c7b7344badccd1502c","tid":49934,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"尼日利亞自殺式炸彈襲擊　兩人彈最細得7歲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">12月11日(日) 18:4</span><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=hXv%2BUXx%2BUxXZMU%2BhvRazTwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=dc8be5ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】尼日利亞東北部一個市集在當地時間周日，遭遇自殺式炸彈襲擊。2名年幼人彈當日引爆身上的炸彈，造成17人受傷，而2名人彈更當場死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n據目擊者札寶（Abdulkarim Jabo）表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">2名引爆炸彈的小女孩只有約7歲至8歲</span>，她們從人力車走出來，並走向售賣家禽的店舖，然後引爆腰纏的炸彈。札寶稱曾試圖和其中一名女孩說話，但她卻沒有回應。襲擊發生之後，緊急救援隊已趕至現場，部分傷者傷勢嚴重。 <br />\n<br />\n上周五，尼日利亞亦有市集遭遇自殺式炸彈襲擊，釀成至少45死，超過33人傷。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161211/mobile/bknint-20161211184000404-1211_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161211%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20161211184000404-1211_17011_001.html&d=hXv%2BUXx%2BUxXZMU%2BhvRazTwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=c5146798\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161211/mobile/bknint-20161211184000404-1211_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩岩now睇到<br />\n原來係上個禮拜既新聞<br />\n有片影住個老豆洗佢地腦<br />\n話會上天堂 唔洗驚<br />\n睇完個人好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9577bfc10a127fcc79af6c3d9f94b8ef3859cfd8","tid":49934,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"處女上天堂比班聖戰士玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c50c3c1fb50e8406642a42855abb78bd4e12a3","tid":49934,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2